受法治威严。2020年至2022年，检察机关起诉未成年人涉嫌利用电信网络实施犯罪7221人。对于主观恶性不大、罪行较轻、属于初犯、偶犯、有积极悔改表现的未成年人，在依法从轻处理的同时，“宽容不纵容、严管又厚爱”。2020年至2022年，检察机关对涉嫌帮助信息网络犯罪活动罪的未成年人依法适用附条件不起诉2749人最高检：依法严惩“隔空猥亵”等侵害未成年人犯罪_法治中国_澎湃新闻-The Paper"},"attached_info":"ClQI6tql5fja4ZFhEAMaCDk2NTA5Mzg3IIT126MGMAA4GUArcgk2MDQwMzEzODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"44_1685600217.3101256","card_id":"Q_603245985","target":{"id":603245985,"title":"你学会释怀了吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/603245985","type":"question","created":1685118642,"answer_count":154,"follower_count":162,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[60731,123902,1395652,2390409,2490973],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我想我学会一点点释怀。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I6tql5fja4ZFhEAMaCDk2MzM1MDA0ILK9w6MGMAA4ogFALHIJNjAzMjQ1OTg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"45_1685600217.310617","card_id":"Q_604184178","target":{"id":604184178,"title":"5 月财新中国制造业 PMI 录得 50.9 ，时隔两个月重回扩张区间，如何解读？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/604184178","type":"question","created":1685584429,"answer_count":6,"follower_count":11,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[99,395,922,1740,5582],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"5月财新中国制造业PMI升至50.9 时隔两个月重回扩张区间 6月1日公布的5月财新中国制造业采购经理指数（PMI）录得50.9，较4月回升1.4个百分点，时隔两个月重回扩张区间。"},"attached_info":"ClQI6tql5fja4ZFhEAMaCDk2NTQzMzQzIK3036MGMAA4C0Atcgk2MDQxODQxNzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":fal